dil e nadaan tujhe hua kya hai
aakhir is marz ki dawah kya hai?
Hume unse hai wafah ki ummed 
jinko malum hi nahi wafah kya hai?
Jab jab darad ka badal chaya jab jab ye 
tanha dil ghabraya tab humne dil ko 
ye samjhaya ki akhir dil tu kyun roota hai
duniya me aksar aisa hi hota hai
thoda dhup hai sabka kissa thoda
gum hai sabka hisaa aankh teri bekar 
hi nam hai harpal tu kyun khota hai 
ye dil aakhir tu kyun rota hai?
pighle neelam sa behta hua ye sama
sarsarati hui ye patiya kehrahi hai mujhe
ek tum ho yahan, me hoon aaur mera dil
ek baat hai jo hoto tak aayi nahi kabhi
labz hai o mangti, jiske peeke ke hoto tak aa
jaye mile kabhi o rahe harpal dekhe ye sama ye nighaye
